biz.littlej.jreqs.predicates

Class Predicates

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.littlej.jreqs.predicates.Predicates

  • public final class Predicates
extends Object
    Static utility methods that provide Predicate instances. All methods returns serializable predicates as long as they're given serializable parameters.

    Do a static import of this class and consider its methods as syntactic sugar.

    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Yannick LOTH
